high_descs: Move back then right to the far left countertop left of the sink
Pick up the roll of toilet paper on top of the counter left of the sink
Move to the toilet paper holder on the wall to the right of the toilet
Place the toilet paper on the roll holder on the wall
anns.task_desc: Move toilet paper to the toilet paper roll holder

high_descs: Walk to the sink to your right.
Grab the roll of toilet paper next the the sink.
Turn around and walk to the toilet to your left.
Place the toilet paper on the toilet paper holder on the wall beside the toilet to the right.
anns.task_desc: Place a roll of toilet paper on the toilet paper holder.

high_descs: Move forward and turn to the right to find the sink.
Pick up the toilet paper from the left side of the sink.
Carry the toilet paper and turn around. Move forward and then turn left to face the toilet.
Place the toilet paper on the holder, to the right.
anns.task_desc: Move toilet paper to the holder.
